    "body": "So... I think what we want to do is to have two separate steps for sanity in run_tests.\n\nThe first one calls tools/run_tests/run_sanity.sh. And we remove ./tools/distrib/clang_format_code.sh from run_sanity.sh.\n\nThe second one is ./tools/distrib/clang_format_code.sh, and should have a flag or something that says to NOT run it from within Docker, even if the use_docker option is set.\n\nDoes that sound right ?\n"
